data.description: Welcome to your dream equestrian paradise! This exceptional 20-acre horse property offers the perfect blend of natural beauty and equestrian amenities. Situated in a serene and picturesque location, this property is a haven for horse lovers and outdoor enthusiasts alike. The beautiful ranch style home provides plenty of room for your family to enjoy, complete with a remodeled bathroom, updated kitchen, and a spacious sunroom. Take in the view from the patio while entertaining friends and family in your personal outdoor haven that includes a fully equipped outdoor kitchen. A MD barn featuring 2 12x12, and 2 12x24 stalls with stalls for your beloved horses, providing them with comfortable shelter and ample storage for feed and equipment. This fully fenced and cross fenced property also features a 120X72 ft arena, a round pen, and a large year-round pond. So many opportunities to be had here, including the potential income from horse boarding. Complete with Solar you won't want to miss this gem!
